Package: scclrR
Title: Sparse PFlogPF Normalization and PCA for Seurat Objects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Lior", "Pachter", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "lpachter@caltech.edu"))
Description: R bindings for shifted centered log-ratio normalization
    (PFlogPF) and sparse PCA. The package stores the sparse log-transformed
    matrix and the per-cell centering vector separately, so Seurat workflows can
    use PFlogPF without materializing a dense normalized matrix.
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
